        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>He subsquently becaame a leading animal rights activist, founding Animal Rights International in 1974. The collection contains Spira's notes (handwritten and typed) on dissident activity in the NMU in the 1960s and 1970s, possibly intended for use in a book project. The notes included contact information and rental communications from many NMU insurgents. PLEASE DIRECT FURTHER INQUIRIES TO: peter.filardo@nyu.edu</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <bioghist id="ref3">
